25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%25A3%259D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E8%25B5%25B0&h=dbec8214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201014/s00001/1602661536602/23%E6%AD%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B6%89%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%99%B4%E6%BC%86%E5%A4%A9%E6%8B%BF%E6%B0%B4%E7%AD%89-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E9%81%87%E8%BB%8D%E8%A3%9D%E8%AD%A6%E5%8D%B3%E6%80%A5%E6%AD%A5%E8%B5%B0</a>"},{"pid":"9f9ce6488ff8d16773d6b6b2cd42cfe44f4f8851","tid":2288171,"uid":301666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:59:52.000Z","msg":"被控在2019年11月2日，在葵涌德士古道57至65號地下外，保管一罐噴漆、一把鎚仔、一瓶天拿水、4塊布及一個打火機，意圖損壞他人的財產<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70825c3d9277cc8c3f39b928ccaa311a6e908197","tid":2288171,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43917b5b4fd3f2b1cad6d35f2c84a27a7f53635f","tid":2288171,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f35092df6ec2e9db4e9a0a53f118f3d12cee0f9","tid":2288171,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:00:31.000Z","msg":"王詩麗裁判官指出被告對背囊中的物品必然知情，隨身攜帶這些物品亦證明其有短時間內使用的打算，故判被告罪名成立。王官亦指雖然被告未造成傷亡，但只因警員能及時發現，終判其監禁12個月，並拒絕其保釋候上訴要求。<br />\n<br />\n王官裁決時指，本案爭議為被搜出非法物品的物品的背包是否屬於被告，及其是否有犯罪意圖。惟王官指出被告當日背包內有不少東西，若此背包不屬於被告，他必定能從背囊的特徵及重量發現，故認為涉案背囊屬於被告。另外，王官亦指出，被告於公眾地方管有這些有相當重量的物品，他一定有使用的打算，否則不會隨身攜帶。但因無證據顯示被告欲損壞自己的財產，故認為其目標必然為他人的財產。<br />\n<br />\n王官判刑時指，被告所管有的物品能造成嚴重的破壞，其潛在危險不可忽視。並稱被告非少年人，應為自己的行為負責。故為了保障公眾利益，及阻嚇「蠢蠢欲動打算犯案的人」，判刑須具阻嚇性，而監禁為唯一的考慮，終判其監禁12個月。"},{"pid":"1a4442f08a7f9e3d78cd4de0e1bd04ca0eabff41","tid":2288171,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:04:35.000Z","msg":"依d物品咁撚危險不如直接禁售dnlm"},{"pid":"d9d99e8a622e04589d078dddbac1cc90662b6bcd","tid":2288171,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3c62be0e862325ed13355e5be5ef0cc3151329","tid":2288171,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:18:43.000Z","msg":"下級法院證明唔到有需要用就必定係用黎搞人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58fad036c4c1678c44266232a4413abb238558a8","tid":2288171,"uid":269578,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:23:47.000Z","msg":"呢個官係咪覺得 所有管有J既男人都有意圖強姦佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23509f82d128faeff5a038796f451d2791967b6c","tid":2288171,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ecef47de8ed101d8fb1fe528ae1a1af43980f4","tid":2288171,"uid":255789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:42:37.000Z","msg":"新狗官喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7b9da925d5cda2a4352b4de769b7ad67b287a8","tid":2288171,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:44:17.000Z","msg":"罪成+唔畀保=狗官confirmed"},{"pid":"9e97b97e661b0a08ef1e3a850f9dca0c04d93a41","tid":2288171,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"裝修佬大撚把呢啲野啦，唔拉哂佢，屌氣老母"},{"pid":"29cba518ecd7edeefbcfcfdd268b4b82abfd58fd","tid":2288171,"uid":151387,"like":0,"dislike":0